<br>Primary education in Singapore is a key foundational stage that provides students with a holistic education, nurturing their cognitive, emotional, and social development. The primary education system in Singapore is globally recognized for its rigorous curriculum, well-trained teachers, and comprehensive support systems that ensure every child can achieve their full potential. Sing school is established in 1967.</br>
